Painter with feature film and game industry experience.
Worked as concept artist, Art director, environment TD, matte painter and Houdini TD on projects like Robin Hood, Angels and demons, Australia, Prince of Persia and Golden compass in London vfx houses Cinesite, Framestore, MPC.

http://vimeo.com/user7890262

Still primarily painter at heart but with broad knowledge of vfx production always on lookout for new challenges.

Specialties: 3d generalist/Matte Painter /Environment TD/ Houdini TD /Art Director/2D/3D Artist / Modeler / Lighting Artist
-MA in Fine arts: major in painting
